378
00:18:40,152 --> 00:18:41,687
As long as you don't beat me,

379
00:18:41,687 --> 00:18:43,456
I don't give a damn
about the rest.

380
00:18:43,456 --> 00:18:45,424
That's utterly insane!

381
00:18:48,828 --> 00:18:50,963
He really is insane for sure,

382
00:18:50,963 --> 00:18:54,133
but it looks like lady luck
is on our side now.

383
00:18:54,133 --> 00:18:55,735
Let's do it, pops!

384
00:18:56,535 --> 00:18:58,270
‐It is payback time!
‐It is payback time!

385
00:18:58,571 --> 00:19:01,807
Reach, All Simples, All Runs,
Dora Dora Dragon Punch!

386
00:19:02,108 --> 00:19:03,609
<i>East, South, West, North!</i>

387
00:19:03,609 --> 00:19:05,378
<i>King's Tile Draw!!</i>

388
00:19:05,378 --> 00:19:06,412
<i>Excessive tiles!</i>

389
00:19:06,412 --> 00:19:07,146
<i>Lack of tiles!</i>

390
00:19:07,146 --> 00:19:08,948
<i>Foul! Peeping!</i>
<i>Rule Breakers!</i>

391
00:19:09,215 --> 00:19:10,282
<i>‐Double East, Double South...</i>
<i>‐Double East, Double South...</i>

392
00:19:10,282 --> 00:19:11,917
<i>‐Double Reach Kick!!</i>
<i>‐Double Reach Kick!!</i>

393
00:19:12,251 --> 00:19:12,952
<i>We're no small fries!</i>

394
00:19:12,952 --> 00:19:14,320
<i>So don't mess with us!</i>

395
00:19:18,958 --> 00:19:21,093
Now we're all naked.

396
00:19:21,093 --> 00:19:23,462
So let's settle it
with the next game.

397
00:19:25,931 --> 00:19:28,000
<i>I can't lose to these guys.</i>

398
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:30,403
<i>Princess Peacock won't abide losers.</i>

399
00:19:30,403 --> 00:19:32,538
<i>If I lose now,</i>
<i>I'll be killed.</i>

400
00:19:33,439 --> 00:19:35,875
<i>I'll do whatever it takes to win.</i>

401
00:19:35,875 --> 00:19:37,743
<i>Whatever it takes!</i>

402
00:19:43,049 --> 00:19:45,818
Well, I guess
I underestimated you guys.

403
00:19:45,818 --> 00:19:47,019
But this is it.

404
00:19:47,019 --> 00:19:49,422
I'll finish you off
with this one deal.

405
00:19:49,822 --> 00:19:53,426
I'll send both, you and
Kanbéi straight to hell!

406
00:19:54,126 --> 00:19:56,662
<i>I know that I can't win</i>
<i>by playing fair...</i>

407
00:19:57,396 --> 00:19:59,598
<i>but I still have</i>
<i>my final weapon.</i>

408
00:20:01,133 --> 00:20:03,569
<i>Sorry, but you're gonna</i>
<i>have to disappear!</i>

409
00:20:06,372 --> 00:20:07,540
Lethal weapon!

410
00:20:07,540 --> 00:20:09,675
<i>Giant Tiger Illusion Tiles!</i>

411
00:20:11,110 --> 00:20:13,279
<i>I can shuffle</i>
<i>1,000 tiles per second!</i>

412
00:20:13,279 --> 00:20:14,947
<i>There's no way</i>
<i>you can see my moves!</i>

413
00:20:18,217 --> 00:20:19,285
Oh, sorry...

414
00:20:19,285 --> 00:20:22,154
I was sitting for so long,
my legs were starting to hurt.

415
00:20:22,154 --> 00:20:24,623
It wasn't on purpose, really.

416
00:20:25,224 --> 00:20:27,293
Oh man, what a mess this is.

417
00:20:27,293 --> 00:20:28,894
Let's put the tiles back.

418
00:20:28,894 --> 00:20:29,995
I'll help you.

419
00:20:30,429 --> 00:20:31,630
Stop it!

420
00:20:33,699 --> 00:20:34,700
Never mind.

421
00:20:36,769 --> 00:20:37,603
<i>Damn it.</i>

422
00:20:37,603 --> 00:20:40,539
<i>Some of my tiles</i>
<i>ended up in the wrong position.</i>

423
00:20:41,207 --> 00:20:44,343
<i>Especially that row</i>
<i>that the sunglass guy piled.</i>

424
00:20:44,343 --> 00:20:45,945
<i>I have to get it back!</i>

425
00:20:46,812 --> 00:20:47,980
<i>It's all right.</i>

426
00:20:47,980 --> 00:20:50,382
<i>It might take time,</i>
<i>but it's no problem.</i>

427
00:20:50,916 --> 00:20:51,784
Here I come!

428
00:20:52,251 --> 00:20:54,053
Well, bring it on!

429
00:21:03,062 --> 00:21:04,296
What is this called?

430
00:21:04,296 --> 00:21:06,332
Hey, I just... well...
I'm the dealer,

431
00:21:06,332 --> 00:21:09,602
so I was about to discard
one tile and look!

432
00:21:09,602 --> 00:21:11,170
It seems like I win!

433
00:21:11,170 --> 00:21:13,939
See... It's only "all runs" but...

434
00:21:15,341 --> 00:21:16,976
It doesn't matter
what hand it is.

435
00:21:16,976 --> 00:21:19,145
You have a winning tile
from the beginning!

436
00:21:19,712 --> 00:21:21,280
Heavenly hand?

437
00:21:22,314 --> 00:21:24,917
Good fortune bestowed
upon man by Heaven!

438
00:21:26,185 --> 00:21:28,721
Heavenly hand?
Impossible!

439
00:21:28,721 --> 00:21:31,056
How can that possibly be?!

440
00:21:31,857 --> 00:21:34,160
So finally, in the end,
the Goddess of Gambling

441
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:36,996
decided to have a one
night stand with me!

442
00:21:38,197 --> 00:21:39,965
You did it, Hasegawa!

443
00:21:39,965 --> 00:21:42,434
I always knew you had it
in you all along!

444
00:21:42,434 --> 00:21:43,669
How could this have happened?!

445
00:21:43,669 --> 00:21:44,670
Where did I go wrong?

446
00:21:44,670 --> 00:21:46,772
I don't understand
where I went wrong.

447
00:21:46,772 --> 00:21:49,008
<i>...will keep loving me forever.</i>

448
00:21:51,510 --> 00:21:53,412
That's life for you, isn't it?

449
00:21:57,616 --> 00:21:59,084
Say Gin, let's go celebrate

450
00:21:59,084 --> 00:22:01,387
before the Goddess of
Gambling turns away from me.

451
00:22:01,387 --> 00:22:02,688
That sounds good.

452
00:22:02,688 --> 00:22:04,423
How about we splurge
on some Dom Perignon

453
00:22:04,423 --> 00:22:05,591
mixed with Dom Perignon?

454
00:22:05,591 --> 00:22:07,259
Take it easy, you guys.

455
00:22:10,629 --> 00:22:12,565
You useless bastard!

456
00:22:24,577 --> 00:22:27,546
Well then, that's why gambling is...

457
00:22:33,152 --> 00:22:34,286
What happened?

458
00:25:05,204 --> 00:25:06,338
You all flunked the grade.

459
00:25:06,338 --> 00:25:07,806
Come back to class next year!

460
00:25:07,806 --> 00:25:09,742
Everyone repeats the grade!

